            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="https://www.zaobao.com.sg/sites/default/files/styles/article_large_full/public/images/202009/20200922/file7cfpovmw2aestkd0czr.jpg?itok=JsS9aTBQ" title="台湾的C-130运输机9月22日停在澎湖马公空军基地。（路透社）" alt src="https://www.zaobao.com.sg/sites/default/files/styles/article_large_full/public/images/202009/20200922/file7cfpovmw2aestkd0czr.jpg?itok=JsS9aTBQ" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div><figcaption>台湾的C-130运输机9月22日停在澎湖马公空军基地。（路透社）</figcaption>

